## more form http://www.moolenaar.net/habits.html

1.	`gd`---- find declaration of a virable, works for QT variable as well
2.	`%`---- find curly braces pair 
3.	`* + cw + n + .`---- powerful substitution command
4.	`qa + ... + q + @a`---- recording

